Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.49,0:23:16.92,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}奇蹟的蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:20.96,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}あなたへ捧ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:20.96,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}一切都獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:23.26,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}涙のバタフライ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:23.26,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fad(300,300)}淚光的蝴蝶
